{"tid":1140934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"薄扶林西島中學女教師企天台危險位置","createTime":"2019-05-06T06:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T17:12:16.000Z","uid":3090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e455d7206bd3a2aecc300764a89bc9291ccf63f1","tid":1140934,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T06:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6whAXVj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6whAXVj.png&h=6f8857f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女教師送院治理。張培生攝<br />\n<br />\n隸屬英基學校協會的薄扶林域多利道250號西島中學，下午1時半，警方接報一名女教師被發現站在學校天台危險位置，救援人員到場展開游說，女教師情緒最後回穩，自行返回安全位置，由救護車送院治理，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=88eefd71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"5a966a888dae7bd252270164a1712c20ba8311dc","tid":1140934,"uid":63588,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:08:26.000Z","msg":"其實做老師壓力好大 又要對學生 又要面對家長 同事校長又唔知夾唔夾"},{"pid":"307cb330b3f42fcaf11e5c4f7f3e1bac6bfefd51","tid":1140934,"uid":85461,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:10:12.000Z","msg":"國際學校都黎料?"},{"pid":"66b2a1118249a790680ce5424f15fed2031065a4","tid":1140934,"uid":210662,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"5a966a888dae7bd252270164a1712c20ba8311dc","tid":1140934,"uid":63588,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:08:26.000Z","msg":"其實做老師壓力好大 又要對學生 又要面對家長 同事校長又唔知夾唔夾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:10:23.000Z","msg":"行行壓力都大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3b07dfa15a94b4dba0969525813a563ce20762",